Author: pinnekjottt
Text: You could do this, but I think the fact that you even posted means you know you shouldn’t. Obviously it’s not as easy as ‘just don’t do it’, but that’s going to be a whole year of progress thrown down the drain for what? Anyway, whatever you do I hope it turns out okay for you and you don’t fall back into old habits. Wishing you strength and love. Good luck
